column5: Need to know if 8M0031688RevC cable assembly is the right one for 08/200 verardo. As it sits now. the engine and tachometer harnesses have male ends. Before I'm put on hold at merc I'd just ask here first. Also are the plugs mirrored.
I don't have an answer, but maybe this page will help?  http://continuouswave.com/ubb/Forum6/HTML/000894.html
